<app from="#beg0675014" to="#end0675014"><lem wit="#wit.orig">能</lem><rdg resp="#resp2" wit="#wit3 #wit4 #wit1 #wit2">汝能</rdg></app>
<app cb:word-count="107" from="#beg0675011" to="#end0675011"><lem resp="#resp2" wit="#wit.orig">若善男子善女<lb n="0675b02" ed="T"/>人作八曼<note n="0675012" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【宋】【元】＊</note><note n="0675012" resp="#resp1" type="mod">荼【大】＊，茶【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0675012"><lem wit="#wit.orig">荼</lem><rdg resp="#resp2" wit="#wit3 #wit4">茶</rdg></app>羅者，云何建立？復依何法<note n="0675013" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text">起＝趣【三】</note><note n="0675013" resp="#resp1" type="mod">起【大】，趣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0675013"><lem wit="#wit.orig">起</lem><rdg resp="#resp2" wit="#wit3 #wit4 #wit1">趣</rdg></app>
<lb n="0675b03" ed="T"/>無量福，令修行者速證菩提？」爾時如來讚寶<lb n="0675b04" ed="T"/>藏月光菩薩言：「善哉善哉！善男子！<note n="0675014" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text">（汝）＋能【三】【甲】</note><note n="0675014" resp="#resp1" type="mod">能【大】，汝能【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0675014"><lem wit="#wit.orig">能</lem><rdg resp="#resp2" wit="#wit3 #wit4 #wit1 #wit2">汝能</rdg></app>問如是<lb n="0675b05" ed="T"/>甚深之義，而為利益無量無邊有情與安樂<lb n="0675b06" ed="T"/>故，及能淨除三惡趣故，為證無比無上智故。<lb n="0675b07" ed="T"/>汝今善聽。若諸有情纔聞此密言者，得長壽<lb n="0675b08" ed="T"/>樂。</lem><rdg resp="#resp2" wit="#wit5" type="correctionRemark">於是寶藏月光菩薩言</rdg></app>
